# <emoji> <type>(<scope>): <subject line, imperative, no period, ≤72 chars>
#
# [optional body, wrap at 72]
#
# [optional footer: Fixes #123 | BREAKING CHANGE: ... | SAFETY: ...]
#
# Emojis: ✨ feat 🐛 fix 🔧 chore 📝 docs 💄 style ♻️ refactor ⚡ perf
#         ✅ test 🚑 hotfix 🔒 security 🌐 i18n 🗃️ db 🔀 merge
#
# Merge commits (before merging branches / PR completion):
#   🔀 merge: <source> into <target>
#
# Scopes (pick closest): core, ui, audio, settings, combat, wave, shop,
#   enemy, weapon, projectile, arena, build, tests, readme, docs, cursor
#
# Examples:
# ✨ feat(ui): add pause menu shortcut hints
# 🐛 fix(shop): prevent duplicate purchase on rapid clicks
